        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer821234518" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13867808842650724868">I thought the story was powerful and one can’t help but empathize with the characters and what they had to go through as Jews during World War II. It was well written and an interesting story of life for some who came to Israel, still in its infancy, after the war. But somewhere along the line, the narrative got to be repetitive, and I longed for a plot that would have followed the characters after they continued their lives in Israel.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


