<div id="review_690779729" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/690779729" />
    <a title="Christine" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1015705-christine"><img alt="Christine" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1323591177p2/1015705.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/690779729?book_show_action=true">Jul 07, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Christine" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Christine" href="/user/show/1015705-christine">Christine</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer690779729" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9038126498862930703">I was disappointed in this mainly because 90% of the book takes place in the detention center, Atlit, and seemed to go on interminably. I&apos;m sure that&apos;s the way it felt to the inmates, but it made for a very slow, uneventful reading experience. 3.0.</span>
  <span id="freeText9038126498862930703" style="display:none">I was disappointed in this mainly because 90% of the book takes place in the detention center, Atlit, and seemed to go on interminably. I'm sure that's the way it felt to the inmates, but it made for a very slow, uneventful reading experience. 3.0.</span>
